snippet.title: [HINDI] 2025 OnePlus Android BGMS Season 4 | League Week 2 - Day 2
snippet.description:
🔥 Esports Ka Blockbuster shuru ho chuka hai! Players are locked, loaded, and ready to drop into the Battlegrounds — jahan sirf sabse zabardast squads dikhaenge apna asli game ⚡

Welcome to the official livestream of 2025 OnePlus Android Battlegrounds Master Series Season 4 📺
The fight for ₹1.5 Crore prize pool begins — har match mein hoga high-octane action aur dhamakedar clutches!

📅 League Stage Dates: 18 August – 7 September
24 invited teams will battle it out in the league stage —
Top 4 ➡ Grand Finals
Mid 8 ➡ Semi Finals
Remaining 12 ➡ Playoffs

Today’s Matches 🔥
1️⃣ Erangel – BC
2️⃣ Miramar – BC
3️⃣ Sanhok – AC
4️⃣ Erangel – AC

Group A
FS Esports | Medal Esports | iQOO Reckoning Esports | myG Los Hermanos | Team AX | Infinix True Rippers | Likitha Esports | Victores sumus

Group B
OnePlus Gods Reign | META NINZA | iQOO ORANGUTAN | iQOO REVENANT X SPARK | NoNx | MARCOS GAMING | iQOO SOUL | TWOB

Group C

snippet.title: Baahubali - The Epic Teaser | Prabhas, Rana Daggubati | SS Rajamouli | 31st October 2025
snippet.description:
Baahubali The Epic is a combined narrative of the two-part Indian film saga, weaving together the grandeur and drama of Baahubali: The Beginning and Baahubali: The Conclusion into one epic tale.

CAST

Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

CREW

Screenplay & Direction: S.S. Rajamouli
Presented by: K. Raghavendra Rao B.A.
Producers: Shobu Yarlagadda & Prasad Devineni
Story: V. Vijayendra Prasad

snippet.title: 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐢 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐢 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐩𝐚𝐲𝐚 𝐉𝐮𝐤𝐞𝐛𝐨𝐱 𝐒𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 | 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐩𝐚𝐲𝐲𝐚 | 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐞𝐬𝐡 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐢 𝐒𝐩𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐒𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐬 | 𝐕𝐦𝐜 𝐃𝐞𝐯𝐨𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐚𝐥
snippet.description:
𝐀𝐔𝐃𝐈𝐎 𝐂𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐓𝐒 :

𝐒𝐎𝐍𝐆 𝐍𝐀𝐌𝐄 : 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐣𝐢 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐣𝐢 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐩𝐚𝐲𝐲𝐚 𝐉𝐮𝐤𝐞𝐛𝐨𝐱 𝐒𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓

𝐋𝐘𝐑𝐈𝐂𝐒 & 𝐌𝐔𝐒𝐈𝐂 & 𝐒𝐈𝐍𝐆𝐄𝐑  : 𝐀, 𝐉𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘 & 𝐃𝐄𝐕𝐀 𝐑𝐀𝐉𝐔 ~ {𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐦𝐮𝐫𝐮}

𝐒𝐈𝐍𝐆𝐄𝐑'𝐒  : 𝐀, 𝐉𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘 & 𝐑𝐀𝐌𝐀𝐍𝐀

𝐌𝐔𝐒𝐈𝐂𝐈𝐀𝐍𝐒 : 𝐒𝐫𝐢𝐤𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐡 𝐊𝐞𝐲𝐛𝐨𝐚𝐫𝐝
                    𝐏𝐫𝐚𝐬𝐚𝐝 : 𝐓𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐚 & 𝐃𝐡𝐨𝐥𝐚𝐤
                     𝐒𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐮 :𝐓𝐚𝐩𝐞𝐬
                     𝐒𝐮𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐡 : 𝐑𝐡𝐲𝐭𝐡𝐦 𝐏𝐚𝐝𝐬
                    𝐒𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐯𝐚𝐬 : 𝐅𝐥𝐮𝐭𝐞

 𝐏𝐑𝐎𝐃𝐔𝐂𝐄𝐑 : 𝐓𝐍,𝐘𝐄𝐋𝐋𝐀 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘

𝐌𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐜 𝐋𝐚𝐛𝐞𝐥 : 𝐓𝐍𝐘𝐑 𝐌𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐜

𝐒𝐏𝐄𝐂𝐀𝐋 𝐓𝐇𝐀𝐍𝐊𝐒 : 𝐘𝐀𝐃𝐈 𝐌𝐔𝐃𝐈𝐑𝐀𝐉 & 𝐀, 𝐉𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘

  𝐒𝐔𝐁𝐒𝐂𝐑𝐈𝐁𝐄 𝐅𝐎𝐑 𝐌𝐎𝐑𝐄 𝐕𝐌𝐂 𝐃𝐄𝐕𝐎𝐓𝐈𝐎𝐍𝐀𝐋 𝐒𝐎𝐍𝐆𝐒 : https://www.youtube.com/@VMCDEVOTIONAL

localized.description:
𝐀𝐔𝐃𝐈𝐎 𝐂𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐓𝐒 :

𝐒𝐎𝐍𝐆 𝐍𝐀𝐌𝐄 : 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐣𝐢 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐣𝐢 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐩𝐚𝐲𝐲𝐚 𝐉𝐮𝐤𝐞𝐛𝐨𝐱 𝐒𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓

𝐋𝐘𝐑𝐈𝐂𝐒 & 𝐌𝐔𝐒𝐈𝐂 & 𝐒𝐈𝐍𝐆𝐄𝐑  : 𝐀, 𝐉𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘 & 𝐃𝐄𝐕𝐀 𝐑𝐀𝐉𝐔 ~ {𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐦𝐮𝐫𝐮}

𝐒𝐈𝐍𝐆𝐄𝐑'𝐒  : 𝐀, 𝐉𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘 & 𝐑𝐀𝐌𝐀𝐍𝐀

𝐌𝐔𝐒𝐈𝐂𝐈𝐀𝐍𝐒 : 𝐒𝐫𝐢𝐤𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐡 𝐊𝐞𝐲𝐛𝐨𝐚𝐫𝐝
                    𝐏𝐫𝐚𝐬𝐚𝐝 : 𝐓𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐚 & 𝐃𝐡𝐨𝐥𝐚𝐤
                     𝐒𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐮 :𝐓𝐚𝐩𝐞𝐬
                     𝐒𝐮𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐡 : 𝐑𝐡𝐲𝐭𝐡𝐦 𝐏𝐚𝐝𝐬
                    𝐒𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐯𝐚𝐬 : 𝐅𝐥𝐮𝐭𝐞

 𝐏𝐑𝐎𝐃𝐔𝐂𝐄𝐑 : 𝐓𝐍,𝐘𝐄𝐋𝐋𝐀 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘

𝐌𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐜 𝐋𝐚𝐛𝐞𝐥 : 𝐓𝐍𝐘𝐑 𝐌𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐜

𝐒𝐏𝐄𝐂𝐀𝐋 𝐓𝐇𝐀𝐍𝐊𝐒 : 𝐘𝐀𝐃𝐈 𝐌𝐔𝐃𝐈𝐑𝐀𝐉 & 𝐀, 𝐉𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘

  𝐒𝐔𝐁𝐒𝐂𝐑𝐈𝐁𝐄 𝐅𝐎𝐑 𝐌𝐎𝐑𝐄 𝐕𝐌𝐂 𝐃𝐄𝐕𝐎𝐓𝐈𝐎𝐍𝐀𝐋 𝐒𝐎𝐍𝐆𝐒 : https://www.youtube.com/@VMCDEVOTIONAL

snippet.title: Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek - Lyrical | The Devil | Darshan | Prakash Veer | B Ajaneesh Loknath
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe 👉 https://bit.ly/Saregama_Kannada

Presenting the Lyrical of ''Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek'' from the much-awaited film ''The Devil'' featuring Challenging Star Darshan. Shri Jaimatha Combines, in association with Saregama a Yoodlee Films, presents the much-awaited film The Devil. Tune in now and feel the vibe. 

Song Credits:
Song Name : Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek
Music Composed, Arranged & Programmed By : B Ajaneesh Loknath
Singer : Deepak Blue
Lyrics : Aniruddha Sastry
Choreographer : Santhu Master
Additional Vocals : B Ajaneesh Loknath, Aniruddha Sastry & Group
Keyboard : B Ajaneesh Loknath, V Sukumar
Rhythm : Ricky D’Costa, Kalyan Chakravarthy, Sukumar V, B Ajaneesh Loknath
Mixed & Mastered By : Sanjay Kumar M P, Renu Digi Studio, Bangalore
Music Production : C R Bobby, B Ajaneesh Loknath, Abbs Studios Bangalore

Movie Credits:
Starring : Challenging Star Darshan, Rachana Rai, Mahesh Manjrekar, Achyuth Kumar, Sharmila Mandre.
Produced by: J Jayamma & Saregama
Directed by: Prakash Veer
Executive Producer : Thashwini Veer
Dialogue : Kanth Raj S S
Direction Department : Mohan Malagi, M S Abishaik, B. Thimme Gowdaa, Purnima Deshpande, Mallik R, Bharath, Chandrakumar, Yuvraj Hemanth, Sanjana Sudhakarr
Director Of Photography (DOP) : Sudhakarr S Raj
Music Director : B Ajaneesh Loknath, Abbs Studios
Editor : Harish Komme
Art Director : Mohan B Kere
Action Director : Ram Lakshman
Colourist : Ashwath
Post Production : Annapurna Studios
Managers : Suresh K Mysore, Jagadish Rao R.
Still Photography : Kadur Raghu & Kadur Yogi
Lyrical Video : Gowtham Raj (Single Frame Studio)
Poster Design : Ashwin Ramesh (Win Designs)
PRO : Sudhindra Venkatesh

Lyrics:
Rap:
Hey Gijigalakama Rakaa Lakama
Gijigalakama Rakaa
Lights On Andare Lit Aag Battaare
Blockbusterrr Pakka

Generation To Generationu
Mugi Beeltaar Egga Mugga
Aye Chinna Oy Chinna
He Breaks All Time Records

Pallavi:
Nammovrene Nange Bossu
Nanu Badkod For The Fansu
Khaasa Aadre Daasa Naanu
Dosti Nibhaaisu

First Day First Show Theatre Alli
Damaal Dimeel Soundinalli !!
Celebration Maadovr Nijvaad Celebritiesu

Hasividdare Saadhne Maadona
Kashta Padovrge Keerti Nidhaana
Namma Bhaashene Nange Pradhaana
Nera Nudile Helteen Kelanna

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek

Rap:
Hey Gijigalakama Rakaa Lakama
Gijigalakama Rakaa
Lights On Andare Lit Aag Battaare
Blockbusterrr Pakka

Generation To Generationu
Mugi Beeltaar Egga Mugga
Aye Chinna Oy Chinna
Forever Record Breaks

Charanam 1:
Cut-Out Andre Naan Antaare
Daulat Ella… No Chance

Yaariginta Naaven Kammi
Anta Aagu… Advance

Ille Hutti Ille Beledu Niyattaagi Ille Duddu
Oorudhdhaara Maadovr Naavu Pakka Localsu!

Yeshte Saahukaara Idru Oorigoore Kondkondidru
Nanna Preetsovr Maatra Nange Celebritiesu

Yene Aagogli
Cho-Ninna Bidovr Naavalla

Nanna Mansalli
Cho-Hachcheyaagirteev Naavella

Beda Namage Berevr Kathe Puraana
Nera Nudile Matte Helteen Kelanna

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek

|| Rap Repeat ||

Charanam 2:
Oyy
Cho-Yenappa
Actually En Gotta Chinna
Cho-Helappa

Ninna Belavanige Ninna Kaiyyalle
Make Your Future Brightu!
Hit Aagodmele Nam Hudga Annovrge
Don’t Need To Be Sweetu!

Prathibhege Illi Kone Illa..
KaleLyoru Kammi Illa…

Nuggi Neevu Munde Bandu Nintre…
Nimge Yashassu

Akkapakkadavra Maatu Keli..
Addressgildang Aagogbedi…
Nimma Nambirovrigella
Neeve Taane The Bossu!!

Nimma Preetige Chiraruni Naa
Ella Nammovre Anta Baalona

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek!!

|| Rap Repeat ||

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek!!


Label: Saregama India Limited, A RPSG Group Company

To buy the original and virus free track, visit www.saregama.com
Follow us on: YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/user/Saregamakannada
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/Saregamakannada
X: https://twitter.com/saregamasouth

snippet.title: Onbathu Kolum & Vinayagar Songs | ஒன்பது கோளும் & சிறந்த விநாயகர் பாடல்கள் | Vinayaka Chaturthi 2025
snippet.description:
🙏✨ விநாயக சதுர்த்தி 2025 சிறப்பாகக் கொண்டாட, இனிய விநாயகர் பக்திப் பாடல்கள் தொகுப்பு இங்கே. இந்த ஜூக் பாக்ஸில் ஒன்பது கோளும், ஓங்காரமே, மூன்று தமிழ், புனிதம் புனிதம், அருகம்புல்லில், நெற்றியிலே குட்டிக்கொண்டேன், மற்றும் ஜெய கணேசா போன்ற பிரபலமான பாடல்கள் இடம்பெற்றுள்ளன. பூஜை, விழா மற்றும் பக்தி நேரங்களுக்கு சிறந்த தொகுப்பு.

🎶 பாடல்கள் மற்றும் நேரங்கள்:
00:00 – ஒன்பது கோளும் | Onbathu Kolum
13:07 – ஓங்காரமே | Ongarame
17:49 – மூன்று தமிழ் வாங்க | Moondru Thamizh
23:07 – புனிதம் அரசமரம் | Punitham Punitham
27:36 – அருகம்புல்லில் இருப்பது யாரு | Arugampullil
47:40 – நெற்றியிலே குட்டிக்கொண்டேன் | Nettriyile Kuttikkonden
52:58 – ஜெய கணேச பாஹிமாம் | Jaya Ganesa

🌺 இந்த சதுர்த்தியில் விநாயகர் அருள் உங்கள் குடும்பத்திற்கு மகிழ்ச்சி, ஆரோக்கியம் மற்றும் செழிப்பை வழங்கட்டும்.
👉 மேலும் பல பக்திப் பாடல்களுக்காக Like, Share, Subscribe செய்யுங்கள்.

🙏✨ Celebrate Vinayaka Chaturthi 2025 with a divine collection of powerful Ganesha devotional songs. This special jukebox features evergreen Tamil Vinayagar songs including Onbathu Kolum, Ongarame, Moondru Thamizh, Punitham Punitham, Arugampullil, Nettriyile Kuttikkonden, and Jaya Ganesa. Perfect for Pooja, Festive Celebrations, and Bhakti moments.

🎶 Songs in this Jukebox with Timings:
0:00 – Onbathu Kolum | ஒன்பது கோளும்
13:07 – Ongarame | ஓங்காரமே
17:49 – Moondru Thamizh | மூன்று தமிழ் வாங்க
23:07 – Punitham Punitham | புனிதம் அரசமரம்
27:36 – Arugampullil | அருகம்புல்லில் இருப்பது யாரு
47:40 – Nettriyile Kuttikkonden | நெற்றியிலே குட்டிக்கொண்டேன்
52:58 – Jaya Ganesa | ஜெய கணேச பாஹிமாம்

🌺 May Lord Vinayaka bless you and your family with happiness, health, and prosperity this Chaturthi.
👉 Don’t forget to Like, Share & Subscribe for more devotional songs.

https://youtu.be/M5u8SKIHwO8

https://youtu.be/812pzaETsKk

https://youtu.be/vC5ccCMr1QA

Listen to superhit Vinayagar hit song by Srihari Arugampulil irupathu Yaru “PILLAIYARAPPA” | அருகம்புல்லில் இருப்பது யாரு | பிள்ளையாரப்பா | ஸ்ரீஹரி | இங்கே அழுத்தவும்

snippet.title: THE RISE OF HANUMAN | Official Teaser 2 | New Movie | Jai Hanuman
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Alice In Borderland Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
The survival action series "Alice in Borderland" became the most watched Japanese Netflix title by worldwide audiences.

Now, the "games" that took the world by storm begin once again.

In the previous season, Arisu (#KentoYamazaki) and Usagi (#TaoTsuchiya) cleared all of the games and returned to the real world. They have since gotten married and established a happy life together. Their memories of the borderland were erased, but they see glimpses of it in dreams and hallucinations. One day, Usagi, led by afterlife researcher Ryuji (#KentoKaku), suddenly vanishes. At the same time as Usagi's disappearance, Banda (#HayatoIsomura) hands Arisu the final card: the Joker.

The uncharted journey led by the mysterious Joker card is about to unfold...

Season 3 of the Netflix Series "Alice in Borderland" is set for worldwide release on Thursday, September 25, 2025, only on Netflix.

#AliceinBorderlandS3, #AliceinBorderland3, #Netflix

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81682895

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Alice In Borderland Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

When a morbid professor pulls Usagi back to Borderland, Arisu goes after her. But can he survive a new round of deadly games and escape the Joker's plans?

snippet.title: Ufff Yeh Siyapaa Trailer | G.Ashok | A.R. Rahman | Sohum, Nushrratt, Nora, Omkar, Sharib | 5th Sept
snippet.description:
In this uniquely wordless comedy of errors, Kesari Lal Singh (Sohum Shah), a sheepish common man, finds himself entangled in a spiraling mess when his wife, Pushpa (Nushrratt Bharuccha), leaves him - convinced he’s been flirting with their neighbour, Kamini (Nora Fatehi). He hasn’t. But before he can clear his name, a wrongly delivered drug parcel sets off a chain of escalating disasters, the worst of which is a dead body turning up in his home. As Kesari scrambles to fix the situation, another corpse appears - turning his house into a full-blown crime scene. To make matters worse, Police Inspector Hasmukh (Omkar Kapoor) arrives with a personal agenda of his own, only adding to the madness. What follows is a wildly absurd, darkly comic chain of events - unfolding without a single spoken word.

Ufff Yeh Siyapaa releases in theatres on 5th September 2025.

Starring: Sohum Shah, Nushrratt Bharuccha, Nora Fatehi, Omkar Kapoor and Sharib Hashmi
Presented By: Luv Films
Written & Directed By: G. Ashok
Produced By: Luv Ranjan and Ankur Garg
Music By: A.R. Rahman

localized.title: Ufff Yeh Siyapaa Trailer | G.Ashok | A.R. Rahman | Sohum, Nushrratt, Nora, Omkar, Sharib | 5th Sept
localized.description:
In this uniquely wordless comedy of errors, Kesari Lal Singh (Sohum Shah), a sheepish common man, finds himself entangled in a spiraling mess when his wife, Pushpa (Nushrratt Bharuccha), leaves him - convinced he’s been flirting with their neighbour, Kamini (Nora Fatehi). He hasn’t. But before he can clear his name, a wrongly delivered drug parcel sets off a chain of escalating disasters, the worst of which is a dead body turning up in his home. As Kesari scrambles to fix the situation, another corpse appears - turning his house into a full-blown crime scene. To make matters worse, Police Inspector Hasmukh (Omkar Kapoor) arrives with a personal agenda of his own, only adding to the madness. What follows is a wildly absurd, darkly comic chain of events - unfolding without a single spoken word.

Ufff Yeh Siyapaa releases in theatres on 5th September 2025.

Starring: Sohum Shah, Nushrratt Bharuccha, Nora Fatehi, Omkar Kapoor and Sharib Hashmi
Presented By: Luv Films
Written & Directed By: G. Ashok
Produced By: Luv Ranjan and Ankur Garg
Music By: A.R. Rahman

snippet.title: Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha & Pooja Vidhanam | Ganesh Chaturthi Special | Vinayaka Chavithi Songs
snippet.description:
🙏 Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha & Pooja Vidhanam – A divine and sacred guide to performing Vinayaka Chavithi Vratham with proper rituals, mantras, and the traditional story of Lord Ganesha.

Narrated by : Tadala Srinivas, I. Muralidhara Sharma


Celebrate this Ganesh Chaturthi with devotion and learn the correct pooja procedure (Vidhanam) along with the auspicious Vinayaka Vratha Kadha in Telugu. This video is perfect for those who wish to observe the vratam at home with sincerity and faith.

Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha is a central part of the Vinayaka Vratham Telugu tradition, observed with deep devotion during VinayakaChavithi. snippet.title: 👽 Franklin’s Alien Baby Pakroo Saves Earth 🌍✨ GTA 5 Malayalam Story | Shinchan Fun
snippet.description:
Franklin is now a father to an Alien Baby Pakroo 👽👶! After one year, Pakroo grows up like Franklin’s kids and joins their family fun. But suddenly, an evil scientist kidnaps Pakroo! 😱

Franklin, Shinchan, Shirinai, and Konichan Uncle go on a mission to rescue him. Later, an alien invasion begins 🌍🚀 and the aliens want Pakroo to destroy Earth! Will he join them or save his family? ❤️

👉 Watch till the end to see Pakroo’s shocking decision that surprises the aliens and saves the world! 🌟

🔥 Don’t miss this fun family story in GTA 5 Malayalam packed with action, comedy, and heart-touching moments!

➡️ Subscribe for more GTA 5 Malayalam adventures with Franklin, Shinchan & Family! 🎉

#GTAV #GTA5Malayalam #Shinchan #Franklin #AlienBaby #Pakroo #AlienStory

रडु नकॊ बाळा तुझा हट्ट पूर्वीते 
Radu Nko Bala Tujha Hatta Purvite
तुझा हट्ट पूर्वीते बाप्पा ला घेऊन येते 
Tujha Hatta Purvite Bappa La Gheun Yete

बागेत जाते दुर्वा फुल आणिते 
Baget Jate Durva Phul Aanite 
फुल मी आणिते गणपतीला वाहते 
Phul Mi Aanite Ganpatila Vahate 
फुल मी आणिते माझ्या बाप्पाला वाहते
Phul Mi Aanite Majhya Bappala  Vahate 

तुझ्या आवडीचे मोदक तूला खायाला देते 
Tujhya Aavadiche Modak Tula Khayala Dete 
खायाला देते तुझं दर्शन घेते
Khayala Dete Tujh Darshan Ghete 
खायाला देते देवाचं दर्शन घेते 
Khayala Dete Devach Darshan Ghete


हिऱ्या मोत्याची कंठी आणाया बाजारा जाते
Hirya Motyachi Kanthi Aanaya Bajara Jate  
बाजारा जाते कंठी घेऊन येते 
Bajara Jhate Kanthi Gheun Yete 
कंठी घेऊन येते बाप्पाच्या गळ्यात घालते
Kanthi Gheun Yete Bappachya Galyat Ghalate 

रुसू नकॊ बाळा बाप्पाची आरती करिते 
Rusu Nko Bala Bappachi Aarti Karite 
आरती करिते तूला मोदक देते 
Aarti Karite Tula Modak Dete 
आरती करिते बाप्पाचा मोदक देते
Aarti Karite Bappacha Modak Dete

snippet.title: #Video | Kamariya Mein Peer | Khesari Lal New Song | Neelam Giri | New Bhojpuri Song | Bhojpuri Gana
snippet.description:
“कमरिया में पीर” – खेसारी लाल यादव और नीलम गिरी का नया धमाकेदार भोजपुरी गाना, अब आपके लिए हाज़िर है। इसमें है जबरदस्त म्यूज़िक, मस्त अंदाज़ और भोजपुरिया तड़का, जो बना देगा आपको झूमने पर मजबूर!

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Song – Kamariya Mein Peer
Hindi - कमरिया में पीर
Singer – Khesari Lal Yadav & Shilpi Raj
Featuring – Neelam Giri
Lyrics - Nirjala NK
Music – Madhukar Anand

Video Credits:-

Director - Sumit Kumar & Rohit Shetty
Choreographer - Rohit Shetty 
DOP - Jason Nambardar
Editor : Nitin FCP 
Associate Editor : Narendra Jaiswal
Di studio -ARTS FOR PRODUCTION 
Colorist- Kunal Singh
Video by - Sushil Pandey (ZQE Pictures)
Production House: Siddhivinayak Media

Lyrics:-

M
नकीया चढ़वले बाड़ू
मुहवां फुलवले बाड़ू
काहे बिछवना गोरी
अलगे बिछवले बाड़ू
तऽ काहे खिसियालू धनी
कोरवा में आजा 
दऽ ना तनी माजा
F
राते बदन दिहलऽ तोड़ ए राजा
झकझोर ए राजा
कमरीये में पीर बाड़ा जोर ए राजा
============================
M
बोलऽ धनी डाक्टर या बैधा बोलाई
खईबू दवाई कि सूई लगवाई
F
दिनवा में फल फूल विटामीन खियावेलऽ
रात में एनर्जी तू खरचा करावेलऽ
M
हऽ तऽ मजबूरी बुझऽ हई तोहर राजा
सहऽ तनी साजा 
F
बथऽता देह पोरे पोर ए राजा
कमजोर ए राजा
कमरीये में पीर बाड़ा जोर ए राजा
============================
M
बनल मिजाज प्यार उमड़ल बेजोड़ हो 
मन करे रख दी पलंगिया के तोड़ हो
F
खुदही वकील खुदे बनऽ तारऽ जज हो
कहे निर्जलवा बनऽ तारऽ निरलज हो
M
प्यार करे दऽ ना बंद कऽ के दरवाजा
फील करबू ताजा
F
काटी लाल कईलऽ गाल गोर ए राजा
खखोर ए राजा
कमरीये में पीर बाड़ा जोर ए राजा
============================

#bhojpurisong

snippet.description:
➤ Subscribe Now :-   https://youtube.com/@AmritaDixitOfficial?

🎵 #AmarSuhagwaRahe | अमर सुहागवा रहे | New #BolBum Song 2025
🎤 Singer: Amrita Dixit
🌿 Sawan Special Bhojpuri Kanwar Song 2025

🙏 भोलेबाबा की भक्ति में डूब जाइए इस नए सावन गीत के साथ!
अमर सुहागवा रहे – एक भावपूर्ण और श्रद्धा से भरा गीत जो समर्पित है भगवान शिव और सभी भोले भक्तों को। अमृता दीक्षित की आवाज़ में यह गाना सावन के पावन महीने में आपकी भक्ति को और भी प्रबल बना देगा।

📀 Song Details:
• Title: teej ka vrat
• Singer: Amrita Dixit
. writer:  Amrita dixit 
  Music:  chandan singh
.
. Feat: Amrita dixit, saurabh samrat
. Video Director: Naveen kumar singh 
:D O P - nitish jee
.Editor- sanjeev saim
• Genre: Bhojpuri Devotional (teej song)
• Language:  hindi
• Year: 2025

🌸 Specially released for Sawan month and Kanwar Yatra!
👉 इस वीडियो को लाइक करें, शेयर करें और चैनल को सब्सक्राइब करना न भूलें।

🔔 Bell icon दबाएं और पाएं नए सावन गीत सबसे पहले!

snippet.title: Jigar Thakor | Garva Gajanand | ગરવા ગજાનંદ | Video Song | New Ganpati Bapa Song 2025 |Jhankar Music
snippet.description:
Jhankar Music Bhakti Gujarati Presents Ganesha Devotional Song titled Garva Gajanand, Sung by Jigar Thakor, & Penned by Sovanji Thakor, & Music Directed by Vijay Dabhi, Prabhat Thakor Undra
Stay tuned & Subscribe Our Yt Channel to get Notified !!
https://www.youtube.com/c/JhankarMusicGujaratiBhakti  

To Make Insta Reels Click here : https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1741545536478207/

🎧 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐨 𝐕𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐨 𝐂𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐬 : 
♪ Song : Garva Gajanand
♪ Singer : Jigar Thakor
♪ Lyrics : Sovanji Thakor
♪ Music : Vijay Dabhi, Prabhat Thakor Undra
♪ Studio : Jhankar Music Recording Studio - Patan
♪ Producer : Maarss Movies And Music LLP 
♪ Projecy By : Vikaram Abluva
♪ D.O.P : Naresh Patani
♪ Editing : Rishvant 
♪ Production : VAT Digital (Alkesh Abluva)
♪ Poster Design : P.C Patan
♪ Light :  Mehul Abluva
♪ Genre : Devotional
♪ Music Label : Jhankar Music
📞For enquiries and for Song Uploading Contact on this No.: 7383909868

#jigarthakor #ganpatisong #gajandandsong #ganeshasongs #jhankarmusicbhaktigujarati 

Listen and Download Song on : 🎶
♪ I Tunes : https://surl.lu/krzbjw
♪ JioSaavan : https://surl.li/gzxmky
♪ Spotify : https://surl.li/pfrejq
♪ Gaana : https://surl.lt/bsgcej
♪ Amazon Music : https://surl.lu/qazzso
♪ YouTube Music : https://surl.li/ljcqdm
♪ Instagram Reels: https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1741545536478207/
♪ Apple Music : https://surl.lu/krzbjw
----------------------------
Lyrics : Gujarati 

હે ગરવા પાટે પધારો ગણપતિ...(૨)
સુખદાતા દેવ તમે સૂંઢાળા 
હો અવસર આવીને સુધારો
કે સમરું સ્વામી  તમને સૂંઢાળા 
હો ગરવા ગજાનંદ દેવ છો દયાળા 
મૂષક સવારીએ આવજો ઉતાવળા...(૨)
હે રિદ્ધિ સિદ્ધિ ના સ્વામી પધારો
કે સમરું સ્વામી તમને સૂંઢાળા
હે ગરવા પાટે પધારો ગણપતિ 
સુખદાતા દેવ તમે દુંદાળા ...(૨)

હો શેરી સજાવશું સ્વાગતમ્ લખાવુ
હૈયા ના હેતે બાપા તમને વધાવુ 
હો મહેકતા ફૂલડાં મારગે વેરાવુ 
સીમ સીમાડે બાપા સામૈયા કરાવુ  
હો ગરવા ગજાનંદ ગુણ ના ભર્યા
રાખજો બાપા ભયા ધન ના ભંડાર...(૨)
એક દંતા આશરો અમને તમારો 
સમરું સ્વામી તમને સૂંઢાળા
હે ગરવા પાટે પધારો ગણપતિ 
સુખદાતા દેવ તમે દુંદાળા...(૨)

હો શિવ શંકર ને માતા પાર્વતી ના પ્યારા
ગણપતિ બાપા આખા જગ થી ન્યારા 
હો આંગણે બાપા પગલા કરજો તમારા
દર્શન દઈ ને જીવન સુધારો અમારા 
હો શુભ લાભ સાથે કરુ પૂજન તમારુ 
કરજો બાપા સપનું પૂરું સપનુ અમારુ...(૨) 
હે અરજી આટલી હાભલો અમારી
કે સમરું સ્વામી તમને સૂંઢાળા 
હે ગરવા પાટે  પધારો ગણપતિ 
સુખદાતા દેવ તમે દુંદાળા...(૨)
----------------------------
@Jhankar Music Bhakti Gujarati

snippet.title: Sumit Parta - Sabhi Khaas (Official Music Video) | New Haryanvi Song 2025 | Real Music
snippet.description:
Presenting “Sabhi Khaas” – the 2025 Haryanvi Hip Hop Anthem by Sumit Parta. 
Raw bars. Street energy. Real talk. 
This track hits hard with loyalty, betrayal & brotherhood stories straight from Haryana’s rap scene.

With powerful lyrics, heavy delivery, and authentic street-style flow, Sumit Parta turns real-life struggles into a bold hip hop statement. Sabhi Khaas is more than just a song — it’s a reality check on friendship, fake loyalty, and survival.

Blending smooth Haryanvi lyrics with a pan-India rap appeal, this track connects with anyone who knows the grind. If you’re looking for authentic Haryanvi hip hop, Sabhi Khaas is your soundtrack.

Hard Bars. Real Emotions. Pure Haryana Vibes.
This is the voice of new-age Haryanvi rap and Indian hip hop.

🎵 Song Credits:
Title: Sabhi Khaas
Singer & Lyricst: Sumit Parta
Music: Xtacy

Director & DOP: Teji Sandhu
Edit: Navraj Singh
Colourist: Onkar Singh
Production: Ten Plus One Production UK
Line Producer: Mandeep Hundal

Producer: Dinesh Golan

snippet.title: Gajanan Sukh Karta Dukh Harta | Divya Kumar & Rashmeet Kaur | Ravi Singhal, Kunaal Vermaa | Lyrical
snippet.description:
👉🏻 SUBSCRIBE to Zee Music Company - https://bit.ly/ZeeMusicCo 

Song: Gajanan - Sukh Karta Dukh Harta
Music: Ravi Singhal
Singers: Divya Kumar & Rashmeet Kaur
Lyrics: Kunaal Vermaa
Chorus: Rohit Shashtri, Divya Kumar, Anirban Saha, Akshay Kamat
Arrangement: Anirban Saha
Percussions: Dipesh Varma
Flutes: Naveen Kumar
Live Strings: Ravi Singhal, Anirban Saha
Rhythm Recorded @ YashRaj Studios by Chinmay
Acoustic Bass, Guitars, Flutes, String Section and Vocals Recorded @ BIG Music Studios by: Akshay Kamat
Mixed and Mastered @ BIG Music Studios by: Ravi Singhal

Production House: 92.7 BIG FM
Producer: 92.7 BIG FM
Director: Aakash Chohan, Kiran Patekar & Fabian Fernandes

Lyrics: 
Sukh Karta Dukh Harta Vaarta Vighnachi
Nurvi Purvi Prem Krupa Jayachi
Sarvangi Sundar Uti Shendurachi 
Kanthi Jhalke Maal Muktaphalanchi
Jai Dev Jai Dev
Jai Dev Jai Dev 
Jai Mangal Murti, 
O Shree Mangal Murti
Darshan Maatre Mann Kaamna Poorti
Jai Dev Jai Dev

O Gajanan O Sarvatman 
Bappa Tere Naam Dil Maine Hai Kiya 
Bappa Har Pal Mein Maine Tujhe Hai Jiya 
Bappa Mera Saath Jo Tune Hai Diya 
Bappa Teri Karuna Mein Jag Jee Liya 

Ratnakhachit Phara Tuj Gaurikumara
Chandanachi Uti Kumkumkeshara
Hirejadit Mukut Shobhato Bara
Runjhunati Nupure Charni Ghagariya
Jai Dev Jai Dev
Jai Dev Jai Dev 
Jai Mangal Murti, 
O Shree Mangal Murti
Darshan Maatre Mann Kaamna Poorti
Jai Dev Jai Dev

O Gajanan O Sarvatman 
Saara Jag Teri Hi Toh Maya 
Sab Meri Khatir Tu Hi Laya 
Iss Dharti Ka Tu Jo Daata 
Isse Sanwaarunga Hai Yeh Vaada 

Lambodar Pitambar Phanivar Bandhana
Saral Sond Vakratunda Trinayana
Daas Ramacha Vaat Paahe Sadana
Sankati Paavave,
Nirvaani Rakshaave,
Survar Vandana
Jai Dev Jai Dev
Jai Dev Jai Dev 
Jai Mangal Murti, 
O Shree Mangal Murti
Darshan Maatre Mann Kaamna Poorti
Jai Dev Jai Dev
Jai Dev Jai Dev

सुखकर्ता दुःखहर्ता वार्ता विघ्नाची ।
नुरवी पुरवी प्रेम कृपा जयाची ।
सर्वांगी सुंदर उटी शेंदुराची ।
कंठी झळके माळ मुक्ताफळांची ।। 
जय देव जय देव ।

जय देव जय देव जय मंगल मूर्ती, ओ श्री मंगल मूर्ती ।
दर्शनमात्रे मनकामना पूर्ती  | जय देव जय देव ।।

ओ गजानन ओ सर्वत्मन
बाप्पा तेरे नाम दिल मैंने है किया
बाप्पा हर पल में मैंने तुझे है जिया
बाप्पा मेरा साथ जो तूने है दिया
बाप्पा तेरी करुणा में जग जी लिया

रत्नखचित फरा तुज गौरीकुमरा ।
चंदनाची उटी कुंकुम केशरा ।
हिरेजड़ित मुकुट शोभतो बरा ।
रुणझुणती नूपुरे चरणी घागरीया ।। 
जय देव जय देव ।

जय देव जय देव जय मंगल मूर्ती, ओ श्री मंगल मूर्ती ।
दर्शनमात्रे मनकामना पूर्ती  | जय देव जय देव ।।

ओ गजानन ओ सर्वत्मन
सारा जग तेरी ही तो माया
सब मेरी ख़ातिर तू ही लाया
इस धरती का तू जो दाता
इसे सवारूँगा है यह वादा

लंबोदर पितांबर फणीवर बंधना ।
सरळ सोंड वक्रतुंड त्रिनयना ।
दास रामाचा वाट पाहे सदना ।
संकटी पावावे, निर्वाणी रक्षावे, सुरवरवंदना ।।

जय देव जय देव जय मंगल मूर्ती, ओ श्री मंगल मूर्ती ।
दर्शनमात्रे मनकामना पूर्ती  | जय देव जय देव ।।

सुखकर्ता दुःखहर्ता वार्ता विघ्नाची ।
नुरवी पुरवी प्रेम कृपा जयाची ।
सर्वांगी सुंदर उटी शेंदुराची ।
कंठी झळके माळ मुक्ताफळांची ।। 
जय देव जय देव ।

जय देव जय देव जय मंगल मूर्ती, ओ श्री मंगल मूर्ती ।
दर्शनमात्रे मनकामना पूर्ती  | जय देव जय देव ।।

ओ गजानन ओ सर्वत्मन
बाप्पा तेरे नाम दिल मैंने है किया
बाप्पा हर पल में मैंने तुझे है जिया
बाप्पा मेरा साथ जो तूने है दिया
बाप्पा तेरी करुणा में जग जी लिया

रत्नखचित फरा तुज गौरीकुमरा ।
चंदनाची उटी कुंकुम केशरा ।
हिरेजड़ित मुकुट शोभतो बरा ।
रुणझुणती नूपुरे चरणी घागरीया ।। 
जय देव जय देव ।

जय देव जय देव जय मंगल मूर्ती, ओ श्री मंगल मूर्ती ।
दर्शनमात्रे मनकामना पूर्ती  | जय देव जय देव ।।

ओ गजानन ओ सर्वत्मन
सारा जग तेरी ही तो माया
सब मेरी ख़ातिर तू ही लाया
इस धरती का तू जो दाता
इसे सवारूँगा है यह वादा

लंबोदर पितांबर फणीवर बंधना ।
सरळ सोंड वक्रतुंड त्रिनयना ।
दास रामाचा वाट पाहे सदना ।
संकटी पावावे, निर्वाणी रक्षावे, सुरवरवंदना ।।

जय देव जय देव जय मंगल मूर्ती, ओ श्री मंगल मूर्ती ।
दर्शनमात्रे मनकामना पूर्ती  | जय देव जय देव ।।
